description:
Week 49 of a series I'm calling "52 Licks." 1 new jazz phrase for each week.

How did I almost get through the year without some Kenny Clarke??

Here's Kenny playing a slick double-time phrase.  Check it out here:

http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-xWjYMGI3DM

he plays the lick at 10:14

Here's the PDF: http://www.mediafire.com/view/qz33g82kythi4fe/KennyClarkeDblTime.pdf

Good Luck!

Justin
